snippet.title: Sega Genesis Aladdin Playthrough: Part 1
snippet.description:
Part one of a playthrough of Disney's Aladdin for the Sega Genesis, or Mega Drive, by Disney Interactive and Virgin Games.

Aladdin escapes from the palace guards in the first stage, Agrabah Market followed by a short minigame starring his monkey, Abu. Interesting enough, the song of the first level is Prince Ali from the movie.
